# Allowlist for `podman build .` from the repo root. Anything else is wasted
# context, and `terraform/.terraform` points outside the repo, which trips
# podman's symlink check while loading the context.
*
!mise.toml
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!packer
packer/*
!packer/qemu.pkr.hcl
!packer/aws/qemu_host.pkr.hcl
